14. "man" (7) -> subject of "ska" (0 distance)
15. "genast" (8) -> modifies "ska" (1 distance)
16. "sätta" (7) -> infinitive (0 distance)
17. "den" (9) -> object of "sätta" (2 distance)
18. "i" (10) -> preposition (0 distance)
